                    </div>
                    <span>I sat through what seemed like an eternity in 10th grade history listening about everything that had to do with "TR".  Of course, it was boring as heck and I didn't learn a thing.
<br />
<br />Then, I saw this book and it peaked my interest.  I must say that this book is not boring in the least.  If offers remarkable detail and clarity about the great Teddy Roosevelt and his time in the oval office.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">It does not get better than this!</div>
