                    <span>Theodore finally got his biographer in this book. I can not recommend this book highly enough! TR Is a very complex and heroic subject that comes forth clear as a bell. I just wish that he was around now as we need him and his type more than ever! AN OUTSTANDING JOB!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Excellent.  Great fun.</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
